23:["$","p",null,{"children":["適用，步驟大致相同。但本站嘅",["$","a",null,{"href":"/install/macos","children":"安裝教學"}],"係 macOS 版本，Windows 版本有少量指令差異（例如用 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"choco"}]," 代替 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-red-50 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm font-mono text-red-700","children":"brew"}],"）。建議對照官方 OpenClaw 文檔嘅 Windows 部分。"]}]
24:["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"Q：路線全部都係連去呢個網站嘅文章嗎？"}]}]
25:["$","p",null,{"children":"係嘅，全部係本站文章，確保內容同版本同步。如果你需要官方技術文檔（例如 API reference、完整 config 文件），可以去 OpenClaw 官方 GitHub repo。"}]
